select REASON_REJECT
     , count(case when {{First_period}} then 1 end) as count_1
     , count(case when {{First_period}} then 1 end)/
       sum(count(case when {{First_period}} then 1 end)) over (partition by 1) as percnt_1

     , count(case when {{Second_period}} then 1 end) as count_2
     , count(case when {{Second_period}} then 1 end)/
       sum(count(case when {{Second_period}} then 1 end)) over (partition by 1) as perc_2
     , count(case when {{First_period}} then 1 end)/
       sum(count(case when {{First_period}} then 1 end)) over (partition by 1) - 
       count(case when {{Second_period}} then 1 end)/
       sum(count(case when {{Second_period}} then 1 end)) over (partition by 1) as change_perc
    from MART.ANTIFRAUD_TX
    --INNER JOIN ANTIFRAUD.ANTIFRAUD_EVENTS on ANTIFRAUD_EVENTS.TX_ID = ANTIFRAUD_TX.TX_ID
    --INNER JOIN MART.CALCULATIONS_UNIQ on CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.UUID_ANTIFRAUD_CHECK = ANTIFRAUD_EVENTS.id
where ANTIFRAUD_TX.partner_name is not null and
      FINAL_STATUS is false and
      {{PARTNER_NAME}}  and
      {{country}} and
      {{payment_type}} and
      {{kind}} and
      {{mobile_pay_type}} and
      {{widget_id}} and
      {{fiat_currency}} and
      {{card_geo}} and
      {{block_kyc}} and
      {{type_status_antifraud}} and
      {{REASON_REJECT}}
group by 1
having count(case when {{First_period}} then 1 end) > 0 or
        count(case when {{Second_period}} then 1 end) > 0
order by 2 desc

WITH list_users AS (select USER_ID, KYC_START_AT
                        from MART.USERS
                        where KYC_START_AT is not null and
                              KYC_STATUS = 'RED' and
                              REG_SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
                              KYC_START_AT > add_months(current_date, -12) 
                        ),
     status_after AS (select list_users.USER_ID
                           , list_users.KYC_START_AT
                           , apl.LABELS
                      from list_users
                               inner join (select cast(USER_ID as decimal) as USER_ID, LABELS
                                           from raw.SUMSUB__APPLICANT_EVENTS
                                           where ACTIVITY in ('moderator:completed:review') and
                                                 REVIEW_ANSWER = 'RED' and
                                                 is_number(USER_ID)) as apl
                                          on apl.USER_ID = list_users.USER_ID),
     gr_reason AS (select LABELS
                        , KYC_START_AT
                        , USER_ID
                        , REGEXP_SUBSTR(substr(LABELS, 2, length(LABELS) - 2), '([^,]+)', 1, 1) AS part1
                        , REGEXP_SUBSTR(substr(LABELS, 2, length(LABELS) - 2), '([^,]+)', 1, 2) AS part2
                        , REGEXP_SUBSTR(substr(LABELS, 2, length(LABELS) - 2), '([^,]+)', 1, 3) AS part3
                        , REGEXP_SUBSTR(substr(LABELS, 2, length(LABELS) - 2), '([^,]+)', 1, 4) AS part4
                        , REGEXP_SUBSTR(substr(LABELS, 2, length(LABELS) - 2), '([^,]+)', 1, 5) AS part5
                   from status_after),
     gr_r_1 AS (select USER_ID, part1, KYC_START_AT
                from gr_reason),
     gr_r_2 AS (select USER_ID, part2, KYC_START_AT
                from gr_reason
                where part2 is not null),
     gr_r_3 AS (select USER_ID, part3, KYC_START_AT
                from gr_reason
                where part3 is not null),
     gr_r_4 AS (select USER_ID, part4, KYC_START_AT
                from gr_reason
                where part4 is not null),
     gr_r_5 AS (select USER_ID, part5, KYC_START_AT
                from gr_reason
                where part5 is not null),
    union_gr_r AS (select USER_ID, part1
                       from gr_r_1

                       union all

                       select  USER_ID, part2
                       from gr_r_2

                       union all

                       select USER_ID, part3
                       from gr_r_3

                       union all

                       select  USER_ID, part4
                       from gr_r_4

                       union all

                       select USER_ID, part5
                       from gr_r_5)


select part1 as LABEL
     , count(distinct case when {{First_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end) as count_1
     , count(distinct case when {{First_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)/
       sum(count(distinct case when {{First_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)) over (partition by 1) as percnt_1

     , count(distinct case when {{Second_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end) as count_2
     , count(distinct case when {{Second_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)/
       sum(count(distinct case when {{Second_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)) over (partition by 1) as perc_2
     , count(distinct case when {{First_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)/
       sum(count(distinct case when {{First_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)) over (partition by 1) - 
       count(distinct case when {{Second_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)/
       sum(count(distinct case when {{Second_period}} then union_gr_r.user_id end)) over (partition by 1) as change_perc
    from union_gr_r
    inner join MART.users on users.user_id = union_gr_r.user_id
    where {{WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME}} and
    {{USER_DOC_COUNTRY}}
group by 1
order by 2 desc
